Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.470 --> 00:00:04.610
Marla and the treatment of her chronic
diseases can also help us understand

00:00:04.610 --> 00:00:07.270
a key problem in our
healthcare delivery system.

00:00:08.330 --> 00:00:12.820
It's fragmentation, and
lack of coordination, and

00:00:12.820 --> 00:00:15.100
how informatics can help fix that.

00:00:16.180 --> 00:00:20.210
One way is by enabling
a different approach to care.

00:00:20.210 --> 00:00:25.240
Marla may have many problems, but she's
still one person, so her problems need

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:30.450
to be managed in a coordinated way, and
within the context of her capabilities,

00:00:30.450 --> 00:00:34.070
lifestyle, resources,
and social situation.

